Thanks for booking a flight
===============================================

You have successfully booked a ticket for flight #<%= @flight.id %>.
Leaving on <%= @flight.start.to_date %>.
Begin: <%= @flight.from_airport.name %>
End: <%= @flight.to_airport.name %>.
<% if @booking.passengers.many? %>
<%= pluralize(@booking.passengers.count, "Passenger") %>
  <% @booking.passengers.each do |passenger| %>
    <%= passenger.name %><br/>
  <% end %>
<% end %>

To view your booking, just follow this link: <%= @url %>.

Thanks for booking and have a great day!
